Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:59.69,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,538)}與
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:59.69,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(633,538)}別
